    "headline": "IonQ and 5 More Stocks to Play Quantum Fever",
    "summary": "Quantum computing has graduated from a theoretical curiosity to a stock market phenomenon.  Quantum computers, offshoots of quantum mechanics, can explore multiple solutions at once, and promise the kind of processing power that could revolutionize medicine, materials science, and other fields.  The pure-play stocks—the shares of companies that concentrate their efforts wholly on quantum computing—trade mostly on sentiment, since none of the companies have yet to turn a profit.",
